{"tid":471081,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"落街食早餐發覺唔記得帶銀包","createTime":"2017-11-17T02:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T04:47:52.000Z","uid":76570,"like":3,"dislike":139,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"58f276acd199dfbc86ea504d686122b96c0c94c9","tid":471081,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"今日難得放假諗住落街食個早餐 <br />\n行左一陣先發覺自己唔記得帶銀包<br />\n本身諗住返上去拎 但又有一段路 <br />\n醒起手機有支付寶仲有少少錢 走左去ok買左個三文治<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/103252_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F103252_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f75f909d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於第一次用 感覺上同八仔既速度差唔多太概慢1-2秒 唔覺好麻煩好慢<br />\n開始感受到香港人應該要習慣手機支付 由其係男人夏天 著條短褲又要帶多個銀包出街頭真係幾麻煩<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企加兩塊芝士再烘一烘佢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/103236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F103236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9194c87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa91cf48f482e8c53552901fab7d9711a647a4a","tid":471081,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"屌 點解第二張出左其他圖既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/103431_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F103431_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2d780182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4251bd94d6d5ed2060e5e5c4631cac27d1d92a13","tid":471081,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3088927e878e0676f06153515c0ef280802fe95d","tid":471081,"uid":76570,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落街冇錢買麵包</blockquote><br />\n買三文治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d2060c0d04a3822ef85dde79f3c6af7a5341f1","tid":471081,"uid":75466,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"收皮啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"d7d3d0a02b272a38eedd15043941e699f17fbb40","tid":471081,"uid":759,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"試下用支付寶幫你老母買壽衣<br />\n仲爽啊"},{"pid":"a5e79227f1230398bcc620c66b2ff6c4fb0c24dd","tid":471081,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦五毛狗</blockquote><br />\n唔係五毛 如果有其他方便既手機支付app我都好樂意用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb63d8759b66e740bf409347c0c5b435b0d522c","tid":471081,"uid":74405,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"啱呀，不過我用apple pay可以食個麥記珍寶套餐添呀，洗去用支那寶食凍冰冰三文治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff9cd039fdcb1c19b27503f33dc29e5de057413","tid":471081,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱呀，不過我用apple pay可以食個麥記珍寶套餐添呀，洗去用支那寶食凍冰冰三文治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nan機應該用唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f10b16b9d1ed5ac408b0992d2a2837847a1c32","tid":471081,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"有幾撚弱智先會唔記得帶銀包<br />\n另外Apple Pay唔使好似支那寶咁要計住餘額囉"},{"pid":"01a78f1e3464c1e3eb5c0a53438c3667ec8a238b","tid":471081,"uid":2772,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:42:07.000Z","msg